name: Himalayan Salt Stone T light Holder
description:
Small orange streaked saltstone tealight holder.

Natural Himalayan rock salt is recommended  for improving our working and living environments. They are made from natural rock salt crystal which has lain below ground for around 260 million years. It is brought to the surface from depths ranging from 700-1100 meters by traditional mining methods which maintain the benefits of natural salt and which protect it from possible contamination . 

Because all of the work is carried out by hand, and because the crystals are variable, each light is unique in design, colour and weight. The natural substances of salt crystal determine the wonderful look of the crystal. For example, iron imparts a red tone and manganese contributes yellow and orange. 

8cm across x 4cm high

name: Agate totem power stone
description:
The agate totem stone is a representation of an animal which is used amongst tribe people as a symbol of their animal spirit guide.


Discover which animal spirit is your guide by meditating and asking for your animal to join you during the meditation.  Before ending your meditation, always thank your animal for joining you.  By choosing the Totem with your animal spirit guide representation, you will be attracting the gifts of the animal to be with you.

Bear - Power, adaptability, strength, courage, leadership
Cat - Independence, grace, healing, mystery, magic, sensuality
Deer - Love, Kindness, gentleness, dreams, serenity
Eagle - Divine spirit, power, intelligence, understanding
Paw - Alertness, resourceful, balance, fertility, spirit detection, intuition
Rabbit - Shrewdness, transformation, wisdom, healing, new life
Snake - Loyalty, success, perseverance, wisdom, transformation
Wolf - Freedom, success, guidance, magic, friendship, trust

Agate is also a stone of friendship so this makes a wonderful friendship gift. Each stone also comes with a card explaining how to find your animal spirit and what each animals properties are.
